        public void handleOutOfMemoryError(OutOfMemoryError e)
        Try to recover from an OutOfMemoryError by dropping all TraceBufs from the processing queue. Ideally, OutOfMemoryErrors should be prevented by aggressive tuning; this is a last-gasp effort to allow the program to continue running.
